,"avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b450e65e2ca7fd5996be6db49ad013a4","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561222129","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2a1e58383020ca02430ea11700c376c_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545928207,"updated_time":1545928930,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1月1号见证哥德巴赫猜想猜想哈哈，虽然看了n多评论知道了成功几率差多为2的头发数次方分之一，但作为反向机会主义者（瞎编的）我觉得支持一个大家都觉得对的比较没意思。（哈哈哈假如我押对了相当于中了一个不可能得到超级彩票，不是说概率为0不等于不可能发生吗，手动狗头）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎上吵翻天该鼓励或者打击这位同学，嘲讽他和嘲讽鼓励他的和嘲讽盲目嘲讽鼓励他的，再次笑话民科的，各位数学大牛发的也看不懂，假装收藏\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我觉得真的证明出他的错了（万一对了）给个教训就好了，真的沸如江海的评论对于一个未成年来说，还能比较镇定，我叹服他的心理素质，起码这就是很多人做不到的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下图我起码觉得他情商不错，正常高中生应该反驳或者暴跳如雷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人嘲讽有智商就不应该偏科，我对大脑没研究，但也知道历史上很多偏科成才的故事。为什么以前可以，现在不行？你可以嘲讽，但是觉得别人鼓励他就是在捧杀他，未免也太对青年人苛求了吧，键盘打字容易，别人有能力让这个话题火也是你们一做出来的，说到底，说他炒作，火还不得感谢你们？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我个人觉得某些回答大牛所用讽刺手法很有情商，人活久懂得“教训”晚辈还是挺不错的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559954531,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"936ac49d37ccffe05d723c45ff03f161","url_token":"killness-s","name":"Skiiii","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5d962810e84251ec1099f2b5c8829f79_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5d962810e84251ec1099f2b5c8829f79_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/936ac49d37ccffe05d723c45ff03f161","user_type":"people","headline":"前进，不择手段的前进","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559954531","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545796378,"updated_time":1545881597,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":151,"content":"\u003cp\u003e由于眼红题主一个病毒营销式提问直接榨取6000+关注者，再来4000都成大V了，特地提醒各位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关注题主的1月1日看完戏记得取关啊\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主已经万粉了，后面似乎删文章，改名，取关问题，然后就可以开 live 接软广 榨取智商税了。。。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561503140,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"de5155ea09dc18b668db308378010419","url_token":"fancerg","name":"fancerg","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3b88657294f2377c702dc1653e9ddcb8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3b88657294f2377c702dc1653e9ddcb8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/de5155ea09dc18b668db308378010419","user_type":"people","headline":"应用数学系出身程序猿","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561503140","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545973334,"updated_time":1545973334,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e加油，保持对数学学习的兴趣。即使没有进名校，你还有成功的机会。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562600846,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","url_token":"xie-dong-liu-25","name":"叶东流","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","user_type":"people","headline":"自由而无用的灵魂","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562600846","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546107156,"updated_time":1546107156,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e先摆观点：就现在来看，这位同学确实有些不知天高地厚了。不过我们如果嘲讽打击，确实也不应当。把事情讲明白，道理讲清楚，就好，他接不接受那又是另一回事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个其实 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hash=\"77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\"\u003e@Vayne嫒\u003c/a\u003e 这位答主的回答说得很好，高中只是大学的敲门砖，大学才是学术之门的敲门砖，进了学术之门才可能看见哥猜的大门，至于能不能敲开就是你的本事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e到现在，看了很久的戏，也吃了许多瓜，还是忍不住要写点东西。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先声明，我不是学数学的，也不是学理工医科的，不过我们可以类比。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一句证明哥猜相当于什么？各位可以看下面三句话：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①我释读出了十个甲骨文，过几天给你们看，有理有据。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②我能给自由意志与恶的问题做一个逻辑完整自洽的公理化分析，过几天你们看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③我挖出了虞墟，证明了二里头之前的中国北方有国家形态的文明，过几天给你们看考古报告。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①，自从清末民国以来，中国无数文字学家、训诂学家、考据学家、考古学家都想多释读一个甲骨文，现在已经到了瓶颈。别说释读出来了，提出一个有道理的猜想就可以学界瞩目了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②，吵了一千五百年以上的问题，无数哲学家、神学家试图给出一个解答，但到现在为止，没有一个逻辑是没有漏洞的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③，中国人心心念念几千年的事情，现代考古学研究了几十年的事情，夏商周断代工程都做白了一群人的头发，你说挖出虞墟是不是可以让世界震动？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e尽管如此，我还是知道上面三句话的分量其实不会重于证出哥猜，哥猜是数学的皇冠明珠，在许多人看来更有一种神圣性。可能只有自由意志的问题对本学界的学者具有同样的神圣性了。要证出哥猜，需要的智慧也许还要超过你编出一个能蒙骗万千世人的虞墟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们说文人相轻，特别他还是一个名不见经传的高中生，那么他被一群人嘲讽也是正常，不加以打击的话如何显示其所学的专业性？实话说，要是哪个高中生说“我能给古代汉语重新断代，而且证据充足，可以取代现行的几个体系”估计我也会上去骂一顿，人家王力高本汉郑张尚芳那么多大师都扯不清楚的你算个什么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e确实，劝诫和说理就足够了，讽刺还是有些过了。不过我们也要想到一个问题，有些人学了专业数学，甚至就是学数学专业的，当他们看到这么一个可以说是不知天高地厚的回答时，他一定会产生“这个人在侮辱数学界的皇冠明珠”的想法，也难怪他们要讽刺。至于那些毫无知识背景就讽刺的，大家就当是抬杠了，看着好玩随手评几句，其它别管了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后还是希望题主能先想办法进入学术的领域再思考证明哥猜的问题。如果题主都进不了这个领域，那么你证出的可能性大概就是零，那种几何概型里点到一个点的概率，而被众人舆论消费的可能性是一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560311578,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c9d30957c50290f9138c8c1fa021807b","url_token":"yang-zheng-zhu-3","name":"rektboiz","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/6e925f8a2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/6e925f8a2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c9d30957c50290f9138c8c1fa021807b","user_type":"people","headline":"不实名了","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560311578","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545827955,"updated_time":1545827955,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":12,"content":"\u003cp\u003e上清北有一万个方法，你非要挑个最难的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你高中赚一个亿捐栋楼说不定还简单点儿\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557975796,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ab9cc9647685ba81eb6f4f62978cd5b5","url_token":"li-hong-64-89","name":"李虹","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7ba42035c529be83d33f132d01df1ae0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7ba42035c529be83d33f132d01df1ae0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ab9cc9647685ba81eb6f4f62978cd5b5","user_type":"people","headline":"身患罕见病的写作者/公号：罕声","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557975796","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545549970,"updated_time":1545549970,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":20,"content":"\u003cp\u003e上策，给正规的数学类学术期刊投稿，让他们来判断正误。这样最大的可能就是看出一堆错误拒收并且不做任何回应。不要有民科思维，觉得这样就是正统数学界打压你。如果万一真的你是对的，被采用又被全球数学家验证是正确的，那你还想北清吗？哈佛斯坦福不都可以随便进了，想横着走都没关系。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中策，丢掉一举成名的幻想，先在知乎、微信各种自媒体平台自行发表，以作为自己首发证据，然后，该干啥干啥，考不上北清也没关系，反正就是慢慢增长实力，到时候，你就真明白你的证明是对还是错了。如果是对的，再拿出原始文章去震撼天下。还有，一定要多发几个地方，万一有的倒闭也没关系。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下策，走民科道路，炒作。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559689851,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bec1e4a03934bee65b8ca000714c3935","url_token":"chen-xing-yu-35-41","name":"豹子","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bec1e4a03934bee65b8ca000714c3935","user_type":"people","headline":"美国本科生 数学和金融专业","badge":[]